										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>All right, internet, I need your help with this.  Please take a look at these three designs, and tell me which one you like best.  I&#8217;ve been staring at these images for days, and I just can&#8217;t see them anymore.  Or, if you like one part of A, and another part of B, or some such, please let me know that, too.</p>
<p>The cover with the most votes will be the official cover for this book!  Please vote, and be brutally honest in your comments.  Become a Viking today!  (wait, no, that&#8217;s <a title="Vulgar but hilarious game review YouTuber" href="http://www.youtube.com/user/Robbaz" target="_blank">Robbaz</a>&#8230;)  I mean, become a part of the creative process, today!  I really look forward to hearing your opinions!</p>
<h2>       A                    B                   C</h2>
<p><a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-03.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-147 alignleft" style="margin-left:0;margin-right:20px;" alt="Waking Cover A" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-03.jpg?w=200" width="160" height="240" srcset="https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-03.jpg 945w, https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-03-200x300.jpg 200w, https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-03-682x1024.jpg 682w" sizes="(max-width: 160px) 100vw, 160px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-04.jpg" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-148 alignleft" style="margin-left:20px;margin-right:20px;" alt="Waking Cover B" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-04.jpg?w=193" width="154" height="239" srcset="https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-04.jpg 1644w, https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-04-193x300.jpg 193w, https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/waking-cover-proof-04-661x1024.jpg 661w" sizes="(max-width: 154px) 100vw, 154px" /></a></p>
